Nature Bond			KEY:Druid Bear Shaman ~ Nature Bond			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality					DESC:A bear shaman who chooses an animal companion must select a bear. If choosing a domain, the bear shaman must choose from the Animal, Earth, Protection, and Strength domains.
