Greater Deadshot		KEY:Fighter Crossbowman ~ Greater Deadshot	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:At 11th level, when a crossbowman attacks with a crossbow as a readied action, he may add his Dexterity bonus (minimum +1) on his damage roll. This ability replaces armor training 3.	TYPE:FighterArmorTraining_Three
